name: Tengu Panda - KuD-051
description: He has red colored skin and a long prominent nose like emphasizing his character which like an angry and threatening being. they say he used to be an arrogant and proud man in his last life before he is reincanated. Yep, He is reincarnated into a yokai or supernatural spirit. It seems heaven punished him to be like that and he doesnt seems to like it either. He becoming mischievous spirit in the end. Now he live in dense forest or high in the mountain near civilization where sometimes he came down to make a scene with his power.
